{"tid":2447015,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「人們需要音樂」　馬友友接種疫苗後即場演奏回饋醫護","createTime":"2021-03-15T01:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T18:00:41.000Z","uid":36494,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"603bbbb5602a1b498842d23ea57bd167c34d9f1f","tid":2447015,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T01:52:23.000Z","msg":"知名美籍華裔大提琴家馬友友昨天（當地時間 13 日）在美國麻省完成第二劑武漢肺炎疫苗接種。在注射完畢後的 15 分鐘等候觀察期間，他忽然端出大提琴，在現場即席演奏，以回饋醫護人員。許多網民表示感動，說他是個真正的音樂家。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年 65 歲的馬友友 13 日於 Berkshire 社區學院接受注射。從該社區學院分享的影片可以看到，戴口罩的馬友友坐在牆邊，遠離其他接種者進行演奏。演出的樂曲包括 Ave Maria 和巴哈的 Prelude in G Major。演奏完畢後，現場聽眾熱烈鼓掌。據當地疫苗接種團隊指，馬友友是希望「做點回饋」，因此即席演奏。<br />\n<br />\n影片獲網民廣傳。許多人表示欣賞馬友友的演出和善意，稱他是個真正的音樂家。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E4%BA%BA%E5%80%91%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82-%E9%A6%AC%E5%8F%8B%E5%8F%8B%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%BE%8C%E5%8D%B3%E5%A0%B4%E6%BC%94%E5%A5%8F%E5%9B%9E%E9%A5%8B%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7/?fbclid=IwAR1s-OpdjIN7j7o5kzSi75JKBnAdXG-GoA2K2bkwkDTvOBS-n-XPWksePok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2580%2591%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%25A6%2581%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%25A5%258F%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%25A5%258B%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1s-OpdjIN7j7o5kzSi75JKBnAdXG-GoA2K2bkwkDTvOBS-n-XPWksePok&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=60e0b4e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2580%2591%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%25A6%2581%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E7%2596%25AB%